name: i wonder where you are
description:
beautiful clouds shot on fujifilm superia with a canon point and shoot. 

more than a year ago i suffered the loss of a close friend. i had taken this photo before that event, but looking back on it, it was inevitable not to think of him. where are you now? did you find the peace you were looking for? did you regret the choice? things i'll never know, and i just wonder...
